cardhead649@... writes:


&gt; Jackie takes a moment to organize his thoughts.  &quot;Well, there was 
&gt; this Predacon criminal named Megatron - no relation to the original - 
&gt; who escaped from prison and came here with some of his lackeys.  Our 
&gt; original mission was to find and arrest him.  But another group of 
&gt; Predacons turned up led by Galvatron - the mutated nutcase that 
&gt; Unicron made of the original Megatron.  He&#39;d been reformatted to a 
&gt; Pred himself and the two got into a fight.  There was an accident, 
&gt; and the two fused.  Boom!  Instant super-robot!  And Hydras is, from 
&gt; what I&#39;ve seen, even crazier than his component parts.&quot;
&gt; 

Standing still, she pondered & let sink in what Wheeljack said. &#39;Functioning? 
How?&#39; Last she knew.. they... he.. was terminated... gone. & another 
Megatron. How could there be another? This made her far more curious. 
Questions arose that she wanted answered. One way or another, she would have 
them. 

Seemed she would find this Hydras & find out what was going on. But... not 
show herself until she gained her old form back. Perhaps, if there was any 
memories in Hydras of Megatron&#39;s & Galvatron&#39;s, then he would surely know who 
she was. But for now... in this updated Beast Machine form, she would 
observe. AS she would keep a watch upon the Ark. 

&quot;I look forward to my reconstructed form soon. I shall return in a few days.&quot;

She held out a clawed hand to Wheeljack to shake his hand. &quot;Thank you. You 
have earned my respect.&quot; 





